<i>What if I don't behave well?</i>

24
00:01:43,400 --> 00:01:46,200
<i>You want to kill me?</i>

25
00:01:51,600 --> 00:01:53,600
<i>We have signed a blood contract.</i>

26
00:01:53,600 --> 00:01:55,600
<i>You've sold your life to me.</i>

27
00:01:55,600 --> 00:02:00,700
<i>Ning Qing, if you break the contract, you will die.</i>

28
00:02:00,700 --> 00:02:02,800
Of course I won't kill you,

29
00:02:02,800 --> 00:02:04,800
but I can seal you

30
00:02:04,800 --> 00:02:07,400
and keep you in the portrait forever.

31
00:02:07,400 --> 00:02:09,800
<i>Then just seal me.</i>

32
00:02:09,800 --> 00:02:12,600
<i>Why don't you do it?</i>

33
00:02:12,600 --> 00:02:16,200
<i>Because you know that your power was given by me.</i>

34
00:02:16,200 --> 00:02:19,400
<i>If you imprison me, you will imprison your own power.</i>

35
00:02:19,400 --> 00:02:23,400
<i>Ning Qing, we have the same goal.</i>

36
00:02:23,400 --> 00:02:26,400
<i>Anyway, now Lin Haoqing already knows the portrait.</i>

37
00:02:26,400 --> 00:02:28,400
<i>What are you going to do?</i>

38
00:02:28,400 --> 00:02:31,200
<i>Since we want to mess up,</i>

39
00:02:31,200 --> 00:02:33,600
<i>let's mess up to the most.</i>

40
00:03:08,200 --> 00:03:09,600
Put it there.

41
00:03:09,600 --> 00:03:12,800
Don't close the window just because it's too cold.

42
00:03:12,800 --> 00:03:15,200
Falling into the frozen lake will be colder.

43
00:03:51,800 --> 00:03:53,000
Hidden Soul Needle.

44
00:03:53,000 --> 00:03:55,600
Why do you have my aunt's unique weapon?

45
00:03:55,600 --> 00:03:57,400
Aunt?

46
00:03:58,400 --> 00:04:01,200
Qing Shu is Fox King's sister.

47
00:04:01,200 --> 00:04:03,400
You're the daughter of Fox King.

48
00:04:04,800 --> 00:04:08,400
I can explain Qing Shu's death to you.

49
00:04:08,400 --> 00:04:12,000
The spiritual power in my body was given by Qing Shu voluntarily.

50
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:13,300
No way.

51
00:04:13,300 --> 00:04:15,400
My aunt was not related to you.

52
00:04:15,400 --> 00:04:19,000
Why would she give you her spiritual power, which she had cultivated all her life with diligence?

53
00:04:19,000 --> 00:04:22,800
Ji Yunhe, I don't know what forbidden spell you used.

54
00:04:22,800 --> 00:04:25,200
But your Fox Fire just now was so strong.

55
00:04:25,200 --> 00:04:28,800
You can only do that by draining my aunt's spiritual power.

56
00:04:28,800 --> 00:04:30,700
It seems that my cousin was right.

57
00:04:30,700 --> 00:04:32,600
You're the one who killed my aunt.

58
00:04:32,600 --> 00:04:36,200
Today, I'm going to avenge my aunt.

59
00:04:40,400 --> 00:04:42,400
Prince, what are you doing?

60
00:04:46,600 --> 00:04:48,300
Come with me.

61
00:04:59,600 --> 00:05:01,700
She's really a pretty girl.

62
00:05:14,600 --> 00:05:20,000
The remaining days are getting less and less.

63
00:05:26,000 --> 00:05:28,000
Why didn't you let me kill Ji Yunhe just now?

64
00:05:28,000 --> 00:05:30,200
Do you know what she did?

65
00:05:30,200 --> 00:05:33,400
Qing Shu's death has nothing to do with Ji Yunhe.

66
00:05:33,400 --> 00:05:35,800
At that time, I was also in the Thousand Flower Valley.

67
00:05:35,800 --> 00:05:38,500
As she said, Qing Shu took the initiative

68
00:05:38,500 --> 00:05:40,400
to pass on the spiritual power to her.

69
00:05:40,400 --> 00:05:41,600
I don't believe it.

70
00:05:41,600 --> 00:05:43,800
Although through the years, we had not seen my aunt,

71
00:05:43,800 --> 00:05:45,300
we still kept in touch.

72
00:05:45,300 --> 00:05:47,800
I had never heard her mention Ji Yunhe.

73
00:05:47,800 --> 00:05:51,200
How could she pass on her spiritual power to an outsider?

74
00:05:51,200 --> 00:05:53,200
For Lin Canglan.

75
00:06:00,500 --> 00:06:02,800
It's the whole thing.

76
00:06:02,800 --> 00:06:06,200
Qing Shu really died voluntarily.

77
00:06:06,200 --> 00:06:08,800
I thought they were just master and servant,

78
00:06:08,800 --> 00:06:10,600
but now it sounds like

79
00:06:10,600 --> 00:06:13,400
my aunt was just entranced.

80
00:06:13,400 --> 00:06:16,800
Lin Canglan didn't care about and cherish her at all.

81
00:06:16,800 --> 00:06:19,500
The Spiritual Masters are really the best at scheming

82
00:06:19,500 --> 00:06:21,700
and playing with people's hearts.

83
00:06:23,000 --> 00:06:26,000
This is the end of this matter.

84
00:06:26,000 --> 00:06:30,000
If there are still people who disagree, let them come to me directly.

85
00:06:30,000 --> 00:06:35,800
I don't want anyone else to bother Ji Yunhe about this matter.

86
00:06:35,800 --> 00:06:40,900
Prince Chang Yi, what's going on between you and Ji Yunhe?

87
00:06:40,900 --> 00:06:42,600
You said she tried to kill you, lied to you,

88
00:06:42,600 --> 00:06:45,300
caused your father's death, and caused the East Sea to be sealed.

89
00:06:45,300 --> 00:06:48,000
So you hate her to the bone and just want to kill her.

90
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:51,400
But why were you so nervous protecting her?

91
00:06:54,000 --> 00:06:58,500
Are you entranced by the Spiritual Master just like my aunt?

92
00:07:02,700 --> 00:07:06,000
I want her to suffer what I have suffered.

93
00:07:06,000 --> 00:07:08,600
So she must survive.

94
00:07:10,400 --> 00:07:12,000
The token.

95
00:07:24,800 --> 00:07:29,000
I insisted on asking Wei Yan for this, so don't blame her.

96
00:07:29,000 --> 00:07:31,000
From now on, no one is allowed to

97
00:07:31,000 --> 00:07:32,800
enter the Cloud Quarters on Lake Island.

98
00:07:32,800 --> 00:07:35,400
I will arrange everything about Ji Yunhe.

99
00:07:35,400 --> 00:07:37,900
She is my prisoner alone.

100
00:07:51,800 --> 00:07:53,600
Qing Yao.

101
00:07:56,200 --> 00:07:58,600
Young Lord, as long as you give the order,

102
00:07:58,600 --> 00:08:01,100
we will go to Lake Island and kill Ji Yunhe.

103
00:08:01,100 --> 00:08:02,600
<i>- Yes.
- Yes, right.</i>

104
00:08:02,600 --> 00:08:03,800
<i>Kill Ji Yunhe!</i>

105
00:08:03,800 --> 00:08:05,200
<i>Kill her.</i>

106
00:08:05,200 --> 00:08:07,600
Cousin, did you tell them?

107
00:08:07,600 --> 00:08:11,900
Yes. Aunt Qing Shu's revenge is our revenge. Why can't I say?

108
00:08:11,900 --> 00:08:13,200
All dismissed.

109
00:08:13,200 --> 00:08:15,100
She's not the murderer.

110
00:08:15,100 --> 00:08:16,800
Qifeng, what's going on?

111
00:08:16,800 --> 00:08:17,800
<i>Then who is it?</i>

112
00:08:17,800 --> 00:08:20,100
If it wasn't her, who else could it be?

113
00:08:20,100 --> 00:08:21,800
Ji Yunhe can take away Qing Shu's spiritual power,

114
00:08:21,800 --> 00:08:23,600
then she can take away all of ours.

115
00:08:23,600 --> 00:08:26,100
Keeping such a person in North Abyss, can everyone be at ease?

116
00:08:26,100 --> 00:08:28,200
<i>Yes, can we be at ease?</i>

117
00:08:28,200 --> 00:08:29,400
<i>We can't.</i>

118
00:08:29,400 --> 00:08:33,100
I said that Ji Yunhe is not the murderer.

119
00:08:33,100 --> 00:08:35,400
Why don't you even listen to me?

120
00:08:35,400 --> 00:08:40,100
Cousin, now the Immortal Master is watching, North Abyss is in danger.

121
00:08:40,100 --> 00:08:42,200
Why are you still so reckless?

122
00:08:42,200 --> 00:08:44,200
Am I reckless?

123
00:08:44,200 --> 00:08:47,800
It's obvious that the merman wants to keep Ji Yunhe and makes everyone feel uneasy.

124
00:08:47,800 --> 00:08:49,600
I don't think he deserves to be our commander.

125
00:08:49,600 --> 00:08:51,600
<i>Yes, he's not worthy to be our commander.</i>

126
00:08:51,600 --> 00:08:52,700
<i>He shouldn't be our commander.</i>

127
00:08:52,700 --> 00:08:55,400
Sowing discord and disturbing the army, you can't be forgiven.

128
00:08:55,400 --> 00:08:59,000
Come on, take Qifeng away, and confine him for 20 days.

129
00:08:59,000 --> 00:09:01,800
Qing Yao, are you going to do this to me?

130
00:09:01,800 --> 00:09:02,900
Take him away.

131
00:09:02,900 --> 00:09:04,800
Let me go!

132
00:09:28,600 --> 00:09:32,000
While struggling to keep me locked up,

133
00:09:32,000 --> 00:09:35,100
while being criticized at the same time,

134
00:09:35,100 --> 00:09:36,800
